spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: Command
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Command"
updatedAt: 2026-04-22
description: Symfony console commands for operational management of the agent loop.
files[6]{file,type,summary}:
  AgentLoopHealthCommand.php,final class,Reports agent-loop health and effective runtime settings to the console.
  AgentLoopResumeStaleRunsCommand.php,final class,Resumes stale agent runs after worker restart by replaying state and dispatching continuation commands.
  AgentLoopRunInspectCommand.php,final class,"Prints a consolidated diagnostic snapshot of run state, mailbox, and replay integrity."
  AgentLoopRunRebuildHotStateCommand.php,final class,Rebuilds hot prompt state for a run from persisted event history.
  AgentLoopRunReplayCommand.php,final class,Replays persisted run events after a given sequence cursor.
  AgentLoopRunTailCommand.php,final class,Prints the latest persisted events for a run to the console.